'''Arda-sällskapet''' (Swedish:'''Arda Society''') is a Swedish Tolkien society. They are the publisher of the bilingual (English and various Scandinavian languages)  journal [[Arda (annual)|''Arda'']] and ''Arda Philology'' documenting the proceedings of the biennial linguistics conference [[Omentielva]].<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=https://www.tolkienshop.com/contents/en-uk/d261.html|articlename=Arda Society|dated=|website=[https://www.tolkienshop.com/index.html TolkienShop.com]|accessed=24 March 2024}}</ref><ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=https://www.omentielva.com/ardaphil.html|articlename=Arda Philology|dated=|website=[https://www.omentielva.com/index.htm Omentielva]|accessed=24 March 2024}}</ref>
